parameters: "Ao-sama, are you planning to gather the villagers for something?"

"No need to say it, I understand. The consultation is about messy
copulation.. in other words, how to invite Hinori-sama to participate in an
orgy!"
"To think that both Ao-sama and Hinori-sama will dote on me.. "

"I will be your partner for the whole night.. no, for three days and three
nights!"

"Um, sorry to interrupt the excitement.. but there's something I want to
talk about regarding Hinori."
"To be honest, I've been hiding something all this time.."

"..Hinori is a girl.. and my girlfriend. I'm sorry for keeping it a secret
until now."

The frivolous atmosphere from earlier disappeared in an instant. Anger
towards the one who broke the rules, lamentation for being deceived.. and
above all, jealousy burns within me for plotting against me and sleeping
with a young man every night.
"Why.. why did you do something that breaks the rules?"
"I cannot forgive this, I cannot forgive it."

Yuu narrowed her eyes and tightened her lips, expressionless. The
atmosphere of Yuu's expression that Ao had never seen before was not
forgiving no matter what kind of explanation was given. It was so strange
that it wouldn't be surprising if the request to be made from now on was
rejected..

It was the moment when Ao was about to open her mouth, wondering what she
could say to persuade Yuu.

"Affairs between men and women are complicated. The rules themselves are
meant to eliminate elements that disrupt public order, such as
entanglements of passion."
"I see, I understand.. is that so?"

"Please listen carefully, Yuu. Ao-sama and Hinori-sama have not brought any
trouble to the village, have they?"
"However, the act of breaking the rules itself.."

"Therefore, revealing that Hinori is a woman when she is not present here..
could it be that there is some kind of trouble related to such matters in
this village?"
A villager gives a cute and playful wink to Ao.

"..I understand. In any case, there is something that cannot be overlooked
for Ao-sama.. to the point where she wants to borrow our power. Please tell
us more about it."

Letting out a deep sigh, the extreme tension dissipated, and along with
exhaustion, the cold sweat's chill seeped into their body.
"Yeah, it's going to be a long story.. but Hinori.."
